<div class="pd-tree-documentation">

	<section id="overview">
		<h2 class="doc-section">Overview</h2>
		<p>
			<code>PDTree&lt;TItem&gt;</code> is a hierarchical tree view component for displaying nested data.
			It supports lazy loading, keyboard navigation, drag-and-drop, inline editing, and customizable node templates.
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Lazy loading</strong> - Load child nodes on demand</li>
			<li><strong>Selection</strong> - Single and multi-select modes</li>
			<li><strong>Drag & drop</strong> - Reorder and move nodes</li>
			<li><strong>Inline editing</strong> - Rename nodes in place</li>
			<li><strong>Keyboard navigation</strong> - Arrow keys, Enter, Delete</li>
			<li><strong>Custom icons</strong> - Per-node icon customization</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

